# Discord Chat Analysis for "core-devs" Channel

## 1. Summary
The chat segment is brief and contains minimal technical discussion. The main technical point involves updating plugins to newer versions, specifically mentioning the need for "v5 everywhere" and a planned effort to update all plugins with Zod v4, AISDK v5, and triple build support (ESM, CJS, and browser) with package.json exports configuration. There's also a mention of a GitHub PR (#40) for the plugin-knowledge repository. Additionally, someone shared a link to a vending machine benchmark/evaluation that could potentially be adapted for commerce evaluation purposes.
